<body>

<header>
  <div class="brand">WastedToken Mint<span>fine challenge coins &amp; medals</span></div>
  <nav>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#collection">Collection</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <div class="eyebrow">Est. 2024 · Struck, not printed</div>
    <h1>Coins that outlast the <em>bar tab</em>.</h1>
    <p>Every WastedToken is deep‑relief struck from solid alloy, hand‑finished, and
       edge‑reeded for that unmistakable clink. This is our flagship strike —
