<section class="about" id="about">
  <h2>About the Mint</h2>
  <p class="lede">WastedToken Mint is a small‑batch coin house obsessed with the
     tactile weight of a real challenge coin. No stamped tin, no printed
     resin — every design is sculpted, deep‑relief tooled, and struck under
     150 tons of pressure before hand finishing.</p>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div>
      <h3>Deep Relief</h3>
      <p>Emblems are sculpted in true bas‑relief, not etched, so every coin
         catches light differently depending on the angle it's held.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>Reeded Edges</h3>
      <p>Every strike is finished with a hand‑set reeded edge — the same
         anti‑counterfeit technique used on minted currency.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>Small Batches</h3>
      <p>We cap every edition. Once a run sells out, that die is retired
         for good — no reprints, no exceptions.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="collection" id="collection">
  <h2>The Collection</h2>
  <p class="lede">Four strikes, four alloys. Claim yours before the die is retired.</p>
  <div class="grid">

    <div class="edition" data-edition="bronze" data-state="available">
      <canvas class="edition-canvas"></canvas>
      <h3>Bronze Strike</h3>
      <div class="price">$49 · Unlimited alloy run</div>
      <button class="buy">Add to cart</button>
